<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
<div class="microsite-column govuk-!-static-margin-bottom-4 govuk-grid-column-one-half">
<p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="k6ktu">Join businesswoman and television personality, Alex Polizzi (Channel 5’s Hotel Inspector), as she follows five UK companies trying to land their first export deal in New York.</p><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="5illh">A media first, 'Big in America' is a documentary series streamed on LinkedIn featuring real UK SMEs as they chase their export dreams.</p><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="80ahv">Supported by the Department for Business and Trade on their mission, will our bold and ambitious exporters succeed in landing the pitch of a lifetime?</p><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="c58gc">From factories and offices in the UK to export encounters on the ground in the Big Apple, which UK business will seal that all-important deal and make it Big in America?<br/></p>
<a class="govuk-button govuk-!-margin-bottom-0" href="https://www.great.gov.uk/microsites/biginamerica/watch-now/">Watch now</a>
</div>
<div class="microsite-column govuk-!-static-margin-bottom-4 govuk-grid-column-one-half">
<div class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-6 great-scaled-full-img">
<img alt="Alex Polizzi" height="393" src="https://paas-s3-broker-prod-lon-8db94025-3db3-41df-9a2a-fbb251b24433.s3.amazonaws.com/images/Alex_P_v1.original.width-700.png" width="700"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    

    
        
<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
<div class="microsite-column govuk-!-static-margin-bottom-4 govuk-grid-column-one-half">
<div class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-6 great-scaled-full-img">
<img alt="Corner bistro NYC" height="393" src="https://paas-s3-broker-prod-lon-8db94025-3db3-41df-9a2a-fbb251b24433.s3.amazonaws.com/images/Corner_Bistro_graded.original.width-700.jpg" width="700"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="microsite-column govuk-!-static-margin-bottom-4 govuk-grid-column-one-half">
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" data-block-key="y0sm5">About the series</h2><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="cd0nv">Big in America is a real life documentary series from the Department for Business and Trade (DBT).</p><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="1biks">Streamed on LinkedIn as a media first, the five episodes feature a diverse range of bold and innovative SMEs from right across the UK as they try to land their first export deal in New York.</p><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="7m295">Designed to entertain and inform, ​each episode follows the SME on their export journey to the Big Apple showcasing the <a class="govuk-link" href="/microsites/biginamerica/export-support/">free support available from DBT</a>. From meetings with mentors and peers right through to their 'big pitch' meeting, viewers are offered an inside view of exporting across a range of industries.<br/><br/></p>
</div>
</div>

    

    
        
<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
<div class="microsite-column govuk-!-static-margin-bottom-4 govuk-grid-column-one-half">
<h4 class="govuk-heading-s" data-block-key="x4qqk">Cast list: featured companies</h4><p class="govuk-body" data-block-key="9ejst">From fintech, tech for bikes and plantable books, here's more about our cast list and the companies that took part.<br/><br/></p>
<a class="govuk-button govuk-!-margin-bottom-0" href="https://great.gov.uk/microsites/biginamerica/cast-list/" target="_blank">Find out more<span class="great-visually-hidden">opens great.gov.uk in a new tab</span></a>
</div>
<div class="microsite-column govuk-!-static-margin-bottom-4 govuk-grid-column-one-half">
<div class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-6 great-scaled-full-img">
<img alt="Tom Willday PITCH graded" height="393" src="https://paas-s3-broker-prod-lon-8db94025-3db3-41df-9a2a-fbb251b24433.s3.amazonaws.com/images/Tom_Willday_PITCH_graded.original.width-700.jpg" width="700"/>
</div>
