                </span>
                <div id="detailed-feedback-received"
                     aria-live="polite"
                     tabindex="-1"
                     class="great-inline-feedback__submission-confirmation great-hidden">
                    <span role="img" class="fa fa-check-circle"></span>
                    <h2>Thanks for your feedback</h2>
